Class PSItemDefSummary

java.lang.Object
  com.percussion.cms.objectstore.PSCmsComponent
      com.percussion.cms.objectstore.PSItemDefSummary
All Implemented Interfaces:
IPSComponent, IPSCatalogIdentifier, IPSCatalogSummary, Serializable, Cloneable
Direct Known Subclasses:
PSItemDefinition
public class PSItemDefSummary
extends PSCmsComponent
implements IPSCatalogSummary

An item definition contains all of the design elements that define what an item is. (May also loosely be called a content type. A new term was used to (hopefully) avoid confusion.) This class provides some key pieces of information about a type that is useful when building UIs. Once the user has selected one of these, the id can be used to get further information.

This class doesn't override the clone method because the clone provided by the Object base class is satisfactory.
